{"product_id":"madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-copy","title":"MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Night Cream 70ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis intense night cream soothes sensitive, easily irritated and redness-prone skin. With extract of algea, hyaluronic acid and jojoba oil, the non-greasy formula works to balance the skin's microbiome and reinforce its lipid barrier. Helps reduce skin reactivity, redness and burning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean face, neck and décolleté every evening. Use in combination with MÁDARA SOS+ Sensitive Moisturiser for the best results.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe) Leaf Juice, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Pentylene Glycol, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Cetearyl Alcohol, Coco- Caprylate, Dicaprylyl Carbonate, Isoamyl Laurate, Aqua, Hydrolyzed Rhodophyceae Extract, Cellulose, Octyldodecanol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Xanthan Gum, Irvingia gabonensis kernel butter, Potassium Hydroxide, Hydrogenated Coco-glycerides, Sodium Hyaluronate, Palmitic acid, Stearic Acid, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Sodium phytate, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49858969731399,"sku":null,"price":42.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-sos-sensitive-night-cream-70ml-476299.jpg?v=1739897244","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-sos-sensitive-moisturiser-50ml-copy","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}